ğŸ”§ Key Components
Authentication System
Username-based login: Uses custom username instead of email

Auto-generated emails: username@glucosetracker.app

Secure password storage: Firebase Authentication handles security

Data Model
javascript
Copy
Download
// User Profile
{
  username: "string",
  name: "string", 
  email: "string",
  createdAt: "timestamp"
}

// Blood Sugar Record
{
  id: "string",
  date: "string",
  beforeBreakfast: "number",
  afterBreakfast: "number", 
  afterLunch: "number",
  afterDinner: "number",
  breakfastMeal: "string",
  lunchMeal: "string",
  dinnerMeal: "string",
  userId: "string",
  createdAt: "timestamp"
}
Firebase Services
recordService.js: Handles all database operations

createRecord() - Add new blood sugar readings

updateRecord() - Modify existing records

deleteRecord() - Remove records

listenToRecords() - Real-time data synchronization

ğŸ¯ Usage
Adding a Record
Click "+ New Reading" button

Select date using the calendar picker

Enter blood sugar readings (at least one required)

Optionally add meal information

Click "Add Record" to save

Viewing Statistics
Average: Overall average blood sugar level

Low: Minimum recorded reading

High: Maximum recorded reading

Total Records: Number of entries

Exporting Data
Click "Export PDF" to generate a printable report

Includes all records with meal information

Formatted for medical professional review

ğŸ”’ Security Features
User Isolation: Users can only access their own data

Input Validation: All form data is validated

Firebase Rules: Database security rules prevent unauthorized access

Password Requirements: Minimum 6 characters

ğŸš¨ Error Handling
Login Errors: Specific messages for wrong credentials, user not found, etc.

Network Errors: Handles offline scenarios gracefully

Validation Errors: Form validation with user-friendly messages

Firebase Errors: Permission denied and network error handling

ğŸ“± Responsive Design
Mobile: Icon-only buttons, optimized touch targets

Tablet: Adaptive layout with readable text sizes

Desktop: Full-featured interface with statistics

