ğŸ†˜ Troubleshooting
Common Issues
Firebase Permission Errors

Check database rules in Firebase Console

Ensure authentication is enabled

Build Errors

Clear node_modules and reinstall dependencies

Check Node.js version compatibility

Login Issues

Verify Firebase Authentication is enabled

Check email/password provider is enabled

Getting Help
Check the browser console for error messages

Verify Firebase configuration values

Ensure all environment variables are set

ğŸ“ Support
For support and questions:

Check the troubleshooting section above

Review Firebase documentation

Check browser console for specific error messages

Note: This application is for personal health tracking and should not replace professional medical advice. Always consult with healthcare professionals for medical decisions.